data.description: Just 8 miles from Letchworth State Park, this property is perfect for those seeking out a comfortable, no muss no fuss living environment. This 4-bedroom 2 bath home exudes warmth and character. Nestled in the charming town of Fillmore, this home is close to Houghton college and other local amenities. This home has been completely renovated from top to bottom. Nothing left for you to do but enjoy it! Outside the home you can enjoy the sounds of the Genesee River from you hot tub! The river runs thought the back of the property alongside the many fruit and nut trees
